- Playground for ball-dominating battles refers to matches where teams aggressively strive for ball possession; 
- Combined possession rates mean adding together the possession percentages of home and away teams; 
- Average total possession is the mean of these combined rates per tournament.

- "embarked on a journey" refers to participating in tournaments;
- "arenas of the millennium" refers to any tournament locations or events that happened in the span between the year 2000 and 2009;
- "setting sail with more than fifty stars in their treasure chests" metaphorically refers to teams accumulating more than 50 points;
- "between the turn of the millennium and the dawn of the decade following" refers to the time period from 2000 to 2009 inclusively.
